The Telegraph - Calcutta (Kolkata) | Nation | Actor remand 
                                                                                                               Actor remand 
                            
	Mumbai, June 18 (PTI) Shiney Ahuja, accused of raping his domestic help, was today remanded in judicial custody till July 2.        
	The 35-year-old actor, who can apply for bail, was remanded after the prosecution said it wanted to investigate if he had consumed drugs or was drunk at the time of the Sunday afternoon incident at his home.                                                                                                                                                                           
